		{"id":"4000000000000012","type":"text","text":"base64 PCM\n`input_audio_buffer.append`","x":500,"y":1060,"width":260,"height":80,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"4000000000000013","type":"text","text":"**Azure Voice Live WS**\n`voicelive_connect` (gpt-realtime)\nServerVad + EchoCancel + NoiseSup","x":780,"y":1040,"width":320,"height":120,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000014","type":"text","text":"**pending function_call**\n`response.function_call_arguments.done`\n→ まず response state に buffer","x":1120,"y":1040,"width":340,"height":100,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000015","type":"text","text":"**McpAdapter** (HTTP `localhost:9990/mcp`)\n→ McpServer → スキル実行","x":1480,"y":1040,"width":340,"height":80,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"4000000000000016","type":"text","text":"`function_call_output` を Voice Live に返す\n`report_after_tools` 対象だけ `response.create(audio,text)` で報告","x":1120,"y":1145,"width":700,"height":70,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000017","type":"text","text":"MovementManager → GO2Connection → 犬","x":1480,"y":1220,"width":340,"height":60,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"4000000000000020","type":"text","text":"**WebInputAudioOnly**\ntext → `human_input` / wav → `web_audio`","x":40,"y":1220,"width":380,"height":80,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"4000000000000021","type":"text","text":"**tool_stream** (progress / log notifications)\nツール進捗を `[tool:name] ...` として注入","x":440,"y":1220,"width":420,"height":80,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"4000000000000030","type":"text","text":"`response.audio.delta`\n(PCM16 24 kHz)","x":780,"y":1320,"width":320,"height":80,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000031","type":"text","text":"**_VoicePlayback**\nsd.OutputStream callback + cancel-queue","x":440,"y":1320,"width":320,"height":80,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000032","type":"text","text":"[スピーカー]","x":260,"y":1320,"width":160,"height":80,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"4000000000000040","type":"text","text":"**バージイン**: `input_audio_buffer.speech_started` →\n`_VoicePlayback.skip_pending()` + `response.cancel`","x":1120,"y":1320,"width":700,"height":80,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"4000000000000050","type":"text","text":"`agent` Out: `AIMessage`(最終テキスト)  ·  `agent_idle` Out: bool  ·  `RESPONSE_CREATED`→False / `RESPONSE_DONE`→True","x":880,"y":1460,"width":940,"height":60,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"4000000000000060","type":"text","text":"**response state machine**\n`_resp_had_audio`\n`_resp_pending_calls`\n`_resp_text_buf`\n`_resp_trigger` = user / tool_result / preface_forced","x":880,"y":1540,"width":360,"height":170,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000061","type":"text","text":"`RESPONSE_DONE`\n→ snapshot + reset\n→ `_on_response_done()` を task で起動","x":1260,"y":1540,"width":260,"height":110,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000062","type":"text","text":"audio 無し user turn\n→ `_force_preface()`\n短い返事を先に強制","x":1540,"y":1540,"width":280,"height":110,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000063","type":"text","text":"その後 pending tools を直列実行\n`発話 → tool 実行 → (必要なら) 報告`\n非 report tool は完全 silent","x":1260,"y":1670,"width":560,"height":110,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000064","type":"text","text":"**バージイン時の解除**\n`_resp_done_event.set()` で\npreface / tool_result 待ちも解放","x":880,"y":1725,"width":360,"height":90,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"5000000000000001","type":"text","text":"**凡例**  ·  紫=合成ルート  ·  シアン=upstream モジュール  ·  オレンジ=★ Voice Live 差分  ·  緑=データフロー / ロボット制御  ·  赤=バージイン制御\n\n**voice-live が agentic-ja と異なる主な点**: \n1) `McpClient + WhisperNode + JapaneseSpeakSkill` を 1 本の `AzureVoiceLiveAgent` に統合 (gpt-realtime / ja-JP-NanamiNeural)  \n2) マイクは `SounddeviceAudioSource` から base64 PCM を直接 Voice Live WS に流す (Whisper を経由しない)  \n3) 出力 TTS は WS から届く 24 kHz PCM を `_VoicePlayback` (sd.OutputStream) で即時再生  \n4) MCP は `function_call` ↔ `function_call_output` で双方向ブリッジ (`McpAdapter` 経由)  \n5) forced-speech: response 単位 state machine が preface 保証と tool 後報告をコード側で制御  \n6) バージイン: 再生キュー破棄 + `response.cancel` + pending waiter 解放  \n7) `SpeakSkill` は SecurityModule のアラート用に残置 (会話 TTS とは独立)","x":0,"y":1880,"width":1860,"height":280,"color":"3"}
	],
